{
  "total_duration": 457.858,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 15.16,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象跨年夜，广场上所有人都盯着同一块倒计时大屏：十、九、八……结果屏幕突然卡住了。手机上的时间已经过了零点，可大屏还停在那里。大家先愣住，然后忍不住笑了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 15.51,
      "end": 36.422,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的故事就是一个旧时代版的“倒计时屏卡住”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall clock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对那时的人，就像今天跨年夜的大屏倒计时、电视直播倒计时或手机倒计时。大家不是去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "办事，而是在一个公共地标下面，一起等新年的第一刻。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 36.771,
      "end": 48.143,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "题目"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A cold welcome"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不只是说天气冷。它把大钟当成一个人：新年到了，大钟却像“拒绝欢迎”新年一样，停在最关键的时刻。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 48.493,
      "end": 68.709,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On Wednesday evening, we went to the Town Hall."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以理解成老城镇里的公共建筑和地标，常常有钟楼或广场。人们去那里，是为了站在同一个公共时钟下面等跨年，不是去排队办文件。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 69.059,
      "end": 88.45,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那天是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the last day of the year"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一年的最后一天，也就是跨年夜。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A large crowd of people had gathered under the Town Hall clock."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "crowd"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一大群人，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had gathered"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示他们在关键时刻之前就已经聚在那儿了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 88.8,
      "end": 110.451,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "大家等着这座公共大钟报时："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It would strike twelve in twenty minutes' time."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strike twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是大钟敲响十二点；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in twenty minutes' time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是再过二十分钟。可是十五分钟过去，到了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "five to twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是 11:55，大钟停了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 110.801,
      "end": 133.209,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最明显的证据是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The big minute hand did not move."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "minute hand"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是钟面上指分钟的长针。大家等啊等，什么也没发生。突然有人喊："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's two minutes past twelve!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "已经 12:02 了。新年早就到了，可这座大钟错过了自己最重要的一次欢迎。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 133.559,
      "end": 141.155,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课先把文化场景放稳：人们为什么要站在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall clock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 141.504,
      "end": 146.866,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为那时大家没有手机，所以公共大钟就是大家共同相信的时间？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 147.216,
      "end": 159.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。以前一个城镇的钟楼，像一个公开的时间信号。跨年夜站在它下面，有点像今天大家看城市大屏、电视主持人、直播间或手机倒计时。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 159.486,
      "end": 165.006,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不能只翻成“市政厅”就结束？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 165.356,
      "end": 179.796,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正是。中文里的“市政厅”很容易让人想到办证、排队、窗口。但这篇里它更像老城镇中心的公共地标。人们不是去办政府业务，而是一起参加新年仪式。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 180.146,
      "end": 187.458,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我还要读懂旧式钟表的时间说法。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "five to twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 11:55？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 187.808,
      "end": 205.456,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，离十二点还有五分钟。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "two minutes past twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 12:02，过了十二点两分钟。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "minute hand"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是长长的分针。孩子现在常看数字时间，所以这里要把 11:55 和 12:02 想清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 205.806,
      "end": 210.324,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以笑点不是“天气冷”，而是大钟没有完成倒计时任务？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 210.674,
      "end": 224.074,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "没错。所有人等公共大钟敲十二点，可它停住了。最后有人看手表发现新年已经到了。尴尬的一刻变成了大家一起笑、一起唱歌的时刻。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 224.424,
      "end": 229.333,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "像一场直播卡住了，但大家还是自己倒数完，然后笑着庆祝？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 229.683,
      "end": 242.083,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很好。这就是现代桥：我们相信一个共同的屏幕或时钟。当它在关键时刻失败，人们先困惑，后来一起把失败变成一个可爱的笑话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 242.433,
      "end": 245.889,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On Wednesday evening, we went to the Town Hall."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 246.239,
      "end": 251.735,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was the last day of the year and a large crowd of people had gathered under the Town Hall clock."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 252.085,
      "end": 255.349,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It would strike twelve in twenty minutes' time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 255.699,
      "end": 260.307,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fifteen minutes passed and then, at five to twelve, the clock stopped."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 260.657,
      "end": 263.537,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The big minute hand did not move."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 263.886,
      "end": 267.102,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We waited and waited, but nothing happened."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 267.452,
      "end": 274.892,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Suddenly someone shouted. 'It's two minutes past twelve! The clock has stopped!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 275.242,
      "end": 279.13,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I looked at my watch. It was true."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 279.48,
      "end": 286.32,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The big clock refused to welcome the New Year. At that moment, everybody began to laugh and sing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 286.67,
      "end": 289.566,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Town-Hall"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个短语："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 289.916,
      "end": 291.644,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Town-Hall"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 291.994,
      "end": 308.465,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "Town-Hall"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇里不是“办事大厅”。它是老城镇里的公共建筑和公共地标，常常有钟楼或广场。大家站在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall clock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面，是为了看同一个公共时钟，一起等新年。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 308.815,
      "end": 311.471,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "crowd"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "crowd"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 311.821,
      "end": 313.357,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "crowd"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "crowd"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 313.707,
      "end": 330.683,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "crowd"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "crowd"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“一大群人”。课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a large crowd of people had gathered"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是很多人已经聚在同一个地方。这里的热闹感很重要，因为倒计时失败不是一个人的小麻烦，而是一群人的共同经历。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 331.033,
      "end": 333.88,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "strike"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strike"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 334.23,
      "end": 335.838,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "strike"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strike"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 336.188,
      "end": 351.868,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "strike"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strike"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是“打人”，而是大钟敲响、报时。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strike twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是钟敲响十二点。大家等的是这个公共信号，可大钟停了，所以题目的笑点才出现。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 352.218,
      "end": 391.065,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的语法不要学成时态表，而要看成一条倒计时线。第一层是关键时刻之前："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a large crowd of people had gathered"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，人群已经聚好了。第二层是当时的期待："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It would strike twelve in twenty minutes' time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，从那一刻看，大钟很快将要敲十二点。第三层是时间流动："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fifteen minutes passed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We waited and waited"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。最后一层是突然发现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's two minutes past twelve!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "新年已经到了。故事好笑，就是因为期待中的公共时间和真实时间错开了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 391.415,
      "end": 411.095,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天这个“公共倒计时失灵”放进现代场景。下面三个空都要填：广场大屏、旧式大钟、新年笑点。你从 word bank 里选短语，重点是说清楚：大家相信同一个倒计时工具，可它在关键时刻停住了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 411.445,
      "end": 422.213,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如一块跨年大屏卡住了，手机却显示已经过了零点。英文可以这样想："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The countdown screen stopped, but the New Year had already arrived."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 422.563,
      "end": 457.858,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Town Hall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "five to twelve"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
